// PriceHistory Endpoints

### Get All Price History
GET http://localhost:3000/api/price-history

### Get Price History by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/price-history/1

### Get Price History by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/price-history/99999

### Get Price History by ID (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/price-history/invalid

### Get Price History by Stove Type
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/price-history

### Get Price History by Stove Type (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/invalid/price-history

### Record Sale
POST http://localhost:3000/api/price-history
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "typeId": 1,
    "salePrice": 5000
}

### Record Sale (different price)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/price-history
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "typeId": 1,
    "salePrice": 7500
}

### Record Sale (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/price-history
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "typeId": 1
}

### Record Sale (negative price)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/price-history
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "typeId": 1,
    "salePrice": -100
}

### Get Price Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/price-stats

### Get Price Stats (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/99999/price-stats

### Get Price Stats (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/invalid/price-stats

### Get Recent Prices (default limit)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/recent-prices

### Get Recent Prices (limit 5)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/recent-prices?limit=5

### Get Recent Prices (invalid limit)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/recent-prices?limit=invalid

### Delete Price History
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/price-history/1

### Delete Price History (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/price-history/99999
